OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776326732
OL,3,CKidlington waste mountain clean-up
OL,4,Cbegins after huge illegal dump
OL,6,FA major clean-up operation has begun
OL,7,Fin Oxfordshire to remove an estimated
OL,8,F21,000 tonnes of illegally dumped
OL,9,Fwaste left behind by criminal gangs.
OL,11,FTrucks have started moving onto the
OL,12,Fsite near the A34 in Kidlington, where
OL,13,Fwaste was dumped across around 8,000
OL,14,Fsquare metres of land beside the River
OL,15,FCherwell - an area larger than the
OL,16,Fpitch at Wembley Stadium.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
