OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776326732
OL,3,CKidlington waste mountain clean-up
OL,4,Cbegins after huge illegal dump
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency says specialist
OL,7,Fcontractors from Acumen Waste Services
OL,8,FLtd will shift up to 30 lorry loads a
OL,9,Fday, removing commercial and household
OL,10,Fwaste including tyres, shredded
OL,11,Fplastic and general rubbish.
OL,13,FThe #8m operation is expected to take
OL,14,Faround six months, as campaigners
OL,15,Fbranded the site an 'environmental
OL,16,Fcatastrophe.'
OL,18,FIt was first reported in June 2025 and
OL,19,Flater shut down by Environment Agency
OL,20,Fofficers in October. No further
OL,21,Ftipping has taken place since then.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776326732
OL,3,CKidlington waste mountain clean-up
OL,4,Cbegins after huge illegal dump
OL,6,FAt one stage, there were fears the
OL,7,Fsite would not be cleared until
OL,8,Fcriminal proceedings had concluded -
OL,9,Fpotentially taking years. But in
OL,10,FDecember, the government intervened
OL,11,Fand agreed to begin removal earlier
OL,12,Fthan planned due to the environmental
OL,13,Fand public safety risks.
OL,15,FInvestigators said the site posed a
OL,16,Fserious fire hazard, with internal
OL,17,Ftemperatures on mild days reaching at
OL,18,Fleast 75C. A blaze, they warned,
OL,19,Fcould have forced the closure of the
OL,20,Fnearby A34, a key transport route.
OL,26,@zD@IOX
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776326732
OL,3,CKidlington waste mountain clean-up
OL,4,Cbegins after huge illegal dump
OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds MP
OL,7,Fsaid the government had stepped in
OL,8,Fbecause of the severity of the risk,
OL,9,Fbut stressed efforts to recover costs
OL,10,Ffrom those responsible.
OL,12,F"In the most extreme cases, and this
OL,13,Fis an extreme case, the government
OL,14,Fwill step up and clear the sites," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"That's the right thing to do because
OL,18,Fthe cost to the local economy ` if we
OL,19,Fhad to close the A34, that would be
OL,20,Freally significant.
OL,26,@vD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776326732
OL,3,CKidlington waste mountain clean-up
OL,4,Cbegins after huge illegal dump
OL,6,F"It's right that we clear this site.
OL,7,FBut what we want to do is recover the
OL,8,Fcost of clearing this site from those
OL,9,Fcriminals."
OL,11,FFour people have been arrested in
OL,12,Fconnection with the illegal dumping,
OL,13,Fand investigations are continuing.
OL,15,FDespite the scale of the site and its
OL,16,Fproximity to the River Cherwell, the
OL,17,FEnvironment Agency says there has been
OL,18,Fno confirmed pollution.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776326732
OL,3,CKidlington waste mountain clean-up
OL,4,Cbegins after huge illegal dump
OL,6,FPreparatory work was delayed because
OL,7,Fof bad weather in Winter, but there
OL,8,Fhad been criticism by local residents
OL,9,Fthat the process was too slow.
OL,11,FMP for Bicester & Woodstock, Calum
OL,12,FMiller, who has been campaigning for
OL,13,Fthe action to begin at pace said:
OL,14,F"It's good to see how well prepared
OL,15,Fthe ground is that has taken time, and
OL,16,Fit's been necessary because this is a
OL,17,Ffloodplain.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776326732
OL,3,CKidlington waste mountain clean-up
OL,4,Cbegins after huge illegal dump
OL,6,F"Now we've got a little bit better
OL,7,Fweather. I'm really hoping they can
OL,8,Fget the trucks out of here as quickly
OL,9,Fas possible and just get this site
OL,10,Fcleared in."
OL,12,FEmma Burns, lead for the Environment
OL,13,FAgency in the Thames Valley, said
OL,14,Fextensive preparation work had made
OL,15,Fthe clean-up possible.
OL,17,F"Preparation is absolutely
OL,18,Feverything," she said. "If we hadn't
OL,19,Fdone this proper preparation, we
OL,20,Fwouldn't be able to respond and act
OL,21,Freally quickly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776326732
OL,3,CKidlington waste mountain clean-up
OL,4,Cbegins after huge illegal dump
OL,6,F"We've also been monitoring through
OL,7,Ffire probes the risk of fire. We've
OL,8,Fbeen using evidence to make sure we
OL,9,Ftake action when we need to."
OL,11,FShe added: "The criminals brought this
OL,12,Fin without regard for the environment
OL,13,For the community. We will not do that.
OL,14,FWe are doing this in a way that takes
OL,15,Faccount of that and will make sure
OL,16,Fthis waste is managed legally."
OL,18,FOxfordshire County Council said the
OL,19,Fstart of the clean-up was a relief for
OL,20,Flocal residents after months of
OL,21,Fplanning between agencies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776326732
OL,3,CKidlington waste mountain clean-up
OL,4,Cbegins after huge illegal dump
OL,6,FThe operation forms part of a wider
OL,7,Fgovernment crackdown on organised
OL,8,Fwaste crime, including new enforcement
OL,9,Fpowers for the Environment Agency and
OL,10,Fincreased use of surveillance
OL,11,Ftechnology.
OL,13,FOfficials say they are also
OL,14,Fstrengthening early intervention
OL,15,Fmeasures, including permit suspensions
OL,16,Fand restriction notices, to disrupt
OL,17,Fillegal dumping networks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
